<p>This addon provides a world-flag component that can display any country/territory's flag in 16x16 or 32x32.</p>
<p>
    Currently, {{countryCodes.length}} flags are supported out of 263 officially assigned codes in the
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-1_alpha-2#Current_codes" target="_blank">ISO 3166-1 alpha-2</a> spec.
</p>

<p>Missing a flag? <a href="https://github.com/rounders/ember-world-flags/issues/2" target="_blank">Report it here</a>.</p>

<div class="flagSearch">
  {{input
    autofocus=true
    placeholder='Find A Flag...'
    value=keyword}}
</div>

<div class="flagList">
  <div class="country header">
    <span class="name" {{action 'sortByName'}}>Country</span>
    <span class="code" {{action 'sortByCode'}}>ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 Code</span>
    <span class="lg">32x32</span>
    <span class="sm">16x16</span>
  </div>
  {{#if countryCodes.length}}
    {{#each countryCodes as |code|}}
      <div class="country">
        <span class="name">{{code.name}}</span>
        <span class="code">{{code.id}}</span>
        <span class="lg">{{world-flag code.id 32}}</span>
        <span class="sm">{{world-flag code.id 16}}</span>
      </div>
    {{/each}}
  {{else}}
    <p>Sorry, no flags were found for that query.</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>
